-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">IPv4 即将迎来付费时代：</span></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1" style="list-style-type: square;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">去年 7 月，亚马逊云科技宣布自 2024 年 2 月 1 日起，所有公共 IPv4 地址将按每小时 0.005 美元的价格收费，<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">约合每月 4 美元，</span>而且无论其是否附加到服务中，都要收费；</span></p></li><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">基于容器的部署平台 Fly.io 也在不久前更新社区公告，称会在 2 月 1 日之后，对每个专用 IPv4 每月收取约 2 美元的费用；</span></p></li><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">开源数据处理服务平台 Supabase 计划推出一个 IPv4 的付费附加服务，每月费用为 4 美元。</span></p></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">随着时间一天天临近，围绕「IPv4 收费，迁移到 IPv6」的讨论愈发激烈。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">近日，开源数据处理服务平台 Supabase CEO 兼联合创始人 Paul Copplestone 也发起一则关于“做好准备，IPv6 即将到来”的呼吁。然而，由于 IPv4 讯息和 IPv6 讯息标头有很大不同，因此这两种协议无法互操作，同时升级到 IPv6 之路也面临多重挑战，甚至在有开发者进行了尝试使用，最终得出一个结论：<strong>IPv6 是一场“灾难”，我们未来虽可以解决困难，但目前准备仍然不足。</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100064879" data-ratio="0.11428571428571428" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="700" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-wrap: wrap;letter-spacing: 0.578px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QuwjkSP1G6wEJHaJCLTONqlcQexqRgJcIICxofIOJs6B6tWBfibb7now/640?wx_fmt=png"></p><h1 style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">全球 IPv4 地址消耗殆尽，升级到 IPv6 提上日程</span></strong></span></h1><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">众所周知，随着互联网的不断发展，设备的数量急剧增加，导致&nbsp;2019 年<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">负责英国、欧洲、中东和部分中亚地区互联网资源分配的欧洲网络协调中心（RIPE NCC）无奈宣布，其最后的 IPv4 地址空间储备池在 2019 年 11 月 25 日 UTC + 1 15:35 完全耗尽，全球 42 亿个 IPv4 地址已分配完毕。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">耗尽之后，</span>对于想要继续使用公共 IPv4 地址的用户而言，他们主要靠回收和未使用地址段的释放才能用上 IPv4，其中这些地址要么来自倒闭的组织，要么来自于那些已经迁移到 IPv6 时不再需要的地址。</span></p><p style="outline: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">不难想象，获取日益稀缺的 IPv4 中间过程变得复杂，成本自然而然涨起来了。</span></p><p style="outline: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">此前，亚马逊云科技也曾透露过，在过去五年中，由于难以获得公共 IPv4 地址，单个地址的获取成本上涨了 300% 以上。</span></p><p style="outline: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">所以正如文章伊始所述，各大公司不得不采取收费政策，一方面为了鼓励大家在使用公共 IPv4 地址时更加节俭，另一方面，想<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;outline: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">要借此推动行业内采用 IPv6。</span></span></p><p style="outline: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">Paul Copplestone 表示，“虽然亚马逊云科技每月收取约 4 美元，对个人来说相对较少，但我的假设是，AWS 是许多基础设施公司（如 Supabase）的基础层——我们为每个 Postgres 数据库提供完整的 EC2 实例，因此这将使我们的 AWS 账单增加数百万美元。”<br></span></p><p style="outline: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">也有一些分析师表示，对于任何规模的 AWS 客户来说，这些费用都可以忽略不计，他们也许都不会在自己的账单上注意到这笔新增的支出。然而，对于许多中小企业和初创企业来说，这笔费用很容易就占到账单的 10-30%。</span></p><p style="outline: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100064883" data-ratio="0.11428571428571428" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="700" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QDyP5HTUOXsPlJWd79yygiasaqXicpN7ibIfqiak5WFpaxE1mGxxpfmMjiaA/640?wx_fmt=png"></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">三种选择</span></strong></span></p><p style="outline: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">那么在避不开这笔费用时，公司又有什么样的方法来尽可能地减少支出？</span></p><p style="outline: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">对此，</span>Paul Copplestone 分享了 AWS 上的基础设施公司的三种选择：</span></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1" style="width: 577.422px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;list-style-type: square;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong>将成本转嫁给客户头上。</strong>这一点<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">其实很好理解，就如 AWS、<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Fly.io 所做的，当涉及到租用或者购买 IPv4 地址时，</span>制定新的收费政策，让客户为此付费买单。<span style="letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">对于一个 IPv4 地址，AWS 新的收费金额为每年 43.80 美元（0.05*一天 24 小时*一年 365 天）。</span></span></span></p></li><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong>提供变通办法（例如代理）。</strong>此外，相关企业也可以为客户提供 IPv4 代理服务，通过代理将 IPv6 流量映射为 IPv4 流量。这种方式允许 IPv6 设备访问 IPv4 资源，同时减少对 IPv4 地址的直接需求；或者通过网络地址转换（NAT）技术优化 IPv4 地址的利用。共享一个 IPv4 地址，同时使用不同的端口来区分不同的服务或用户。</span></p></li><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">只提供 IPv6，希望所有人都能跟上使用。</span></p></li></ul><p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100064880" data-ratio="0.11428571428571428" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="700" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-wrap: wrap;letter-spacing: 0.578px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Q0QtgZAx8xsoTReptvArfwbn9MvHGVfV98Qkl5PMRS6MCt2ljwLJwoQ/640?wx_fmt=png"></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">IPv6 普及存在的挑战</span></strong></span></p><p style="outline: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">从长远角度来看，第三种方式即“只提供 IPv6”是最节约成本、解决后顾之忧的方案。因为作为 IPv4 的替代者，IPv6 提供了更好的支持移动设备、更灵活的地址分配、更简化的头部结构以及更好的安全性。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">更为值得注意的是，IPv6 的地址空间极其庞大，可以提供大约 3.4 x 10^38 个地址，也有不少人调侃道——“<strong>I</strong><strong>Pv6 让全球每一粒沙子都有地址</strong>”，其数量远远超过 IPv4，从而满足未来互联网设备的增长需求。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100064881" data-ratio="0.4573268921095008" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="621" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;text-wrap: wrap;width: 506px;height: 231px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAuiaotBEicBhSxX9xxOqXZZy2K6W44cw4nztgV4XfR0tTnCGKsGlKyteMDJ5EolpKibuTgf6Ffj7JWc8A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">IPv6 的到来显然是件好事，但是据 Google&nbsp;<span style="outline: 0px;">统计的数据显示，IPv6 推出十多年时间，截至 2024 年 1 月 15 日，互联网上使用 IPv6 的用户未达五成，占比 41.23%。</span></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 8px;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100064888" data-ratio="0.6361111111111111" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;text-wrap: wrap;width: 470px;height: 299px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAuiaotBEicBhSxX9xxOqXZZy2KNVmlttdj9jraP4ibVmdJIW8rFvK8OvRKricGWQtTZgpweB4vUQdvMQJg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">至于其中原因，Paul Copplestone 将其归因为两个方面：</span></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1" style="list-style-type: square;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">ISP 支持力不足</span></p></li><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">缺乏工具支持</span></p></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100064886" data-ratio="0.11428571428571428" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="700" style="font-size: 15px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Q0jqAkXB2hEohZkOqYzXVsmJtnNRQncYh54ZQOpcC5ZGSicYFgtBZP4w/640?wx_fmt=png"></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">ISP 支持力不足</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“你的互联网服务提供商支持 IPv6 吗？”</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在 Paul Copplestone 看来，全球采用 IPv6 的最大挑战是 ISP（互联网服务提供商，Internet Service Provider）的支持。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">简单来看，当你输入一个网站的域名时，它会被转换成一个 IP 地址。传统上，这些地址都是 IPv4 地址：</span></p><p class="code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js"><pre class="code-snippet__js" data-lang="css"><code><span class="code-snippet_outer"><span class="code-snippet__selector-tag">example</span><span class="code-snippet__selector-class">.com</span> → 93<span class="code-snippet__selector-class">.184</span><span class="code-snippet__selector-class">.216</span><span class="code-snippet__selector-class">.34</span></span></code><br></pre></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">这些域名最终将被转换为 IPv6：</span></p><p class="code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js"><pre class="code-snippet__js" data-lang="css"><code><span class="code-snippet_outer"><span class="code-snippet__selector-tag">example</span><span class="code-snippet__selector-class">.com</span> → 2607<span class="code-snippet__selector-pseudo">:f8b0</span><span class="code-snippet__selector-pseudo">:4006</span><span class="code-snippet__selector-pseudo">:819</span><span class="code-snippet__selector-pseudo">::200e</span></span></code><br></pre></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">ISP 收到该地址后，负责把所有流量路由到正确的目的地。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">遗憾的是，许多 ISP 还没有为此做好准备——它们需要更新的交换机、更新的软件以及与 IPv4 的互操作性。<strong>所有这些都需要花钱，而在过去 10 年中，这种投资并不值得。</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">如果你的互联网服务供应商不支持 IPv6，当域名/服务器开始解析为 IPv6 而不是 IPv4 时，你将会受到以下影响，以及报一些错误：</span></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1" style="list-style-type: square;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">你在 AWS 中设置了 Web 服务器吗？是的话，你将无法通过 SSH 连接到它。</span></p></li><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">你是否使用直接连接从本地计算机连接到 Supabase 数据库？是的话，你需要使用连接池，它将解析为 IPv4（供应商将为这些 IPv4 地址付费）。</span></p></li><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">你是从 Vercel 连接到任何 AWS 服务器的吗？如果不为服务器设置 IPv4 地址，连接很快就会失败。</span></p></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100064884" data-ratio="0.11428571428571428" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="700" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Q3SAo8dibFicWvibnB5u4gdHLgb2AbA6UJ8VImKnyW92hibqZefwpDbPYAQ/640?wx_fmt=png"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">缺乏工具支持</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">此外，许多开发者工具都还没有针对 IPv6 进行设置。<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Paul Copplestone 使用自家的开源 Firebase 替代方案</span>&nbsp;Supabase 来举例说明，他们的数据团队要想<span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">他们的工具链支持 IPv6，</span>需要进行以下更改：</span></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1" style="list-style-type: square;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">为 VPC 网络添加 IPv6 支持。</span></p></li><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">为 Airflow VM 添加 IPv6 支持。</span></p></li><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">为 Docker 和 Compose 添加 IPv6 支持。</span></p></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这些看起来都很简单的一句话，但要真正地实现，非常麻烦。下面是配置 Docker 的步骤：</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">1. 更新 /etc/docker/daemon.json：</span></p><p class="code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js"><pre class="code-snippet__js" data-lang="javascript"><code><span class="code-snippet_outer"><span class="code-snippet__string">"ipv6"</span>: <span class="code-snippet__literal">true</span>,<span class="code-snippet__string">"fixed-cidr-v6"</span>: <span class="code-snippet__string">"fd00:ffff::/80"</span>,<span class="code-snippet__string">"ip6tables"</span>: <span class="code-snippet__literal">true</span>,<span class="code-snippet__string">"experimental"</span>: <span class="code-snippet__literal">true</span></span></code><br></pre></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2. 重新启动 Docker 服务：</span></p><p class="code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js"><pre class="code-snippet__js" data-lang="nginx"><code><span class="code-snippet_outer"><span class="code-snippet__attribute">systemctl</span> restart docker</span></code><br></pre></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3. 创建一个临时 IPv6 网络并进行测试：</span></p><p class="code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js"><pre class="code-snippet__js" data-lang="sql"><code><span class="code-snippet_outer">docker network <span class="code-snippet__keyword">create</span> <span class="code-snippet__comment">--ipv6 --subnet fd00:ffff::/80 ip6netdocker run --rm -it --network ip6net busybox ping6 google.com -c3</span></span></code><br></pre></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">4. 检查 IPv6 iptables 配置（FORWARD）</span></p><p class="code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js"><pre class="code-snippet__js" data-lang="nginx"><code><span class="code-snippet_outer"><span class="code-snippet__attribute">ip6tables</span> -L</span></code><br></pre></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">5. 添加 IPv6 网络配置到组成配置文件 docker-compose.yaml 中</span></p><p class="code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js"><pre class="code-snippet__js" data-lang="properties"><code><span class="code-snippet_outer"><span class="code-snippet__comment"># enable IPv6 to default networknetworks:  default:    enable_ipv6: true    ipam:      config:        - subnet: fd00:c16a:601e::/80          gateway: fd00:c16a:601e::1</span></span></code><br></pre></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">6. 检查是否在容器中运行</span></p><p class="code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js"><pre class="code-snippet__js" data-lang="javascript"><code><span class="code-snippet_outer">docker exec -it <span class="code-snippet__string">"airflow_airflow-worker_1"</span> bashcurl <span class="code-snippet__number">-6</span> https:<span class="code-snippet__comment">//ifconfig.co/ip</span></span></code><br></pre></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">对于像 Docker 这样无处不在的工具来说，这实在是太复杂了。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100064885" data-ratio="0.11428571428571428" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="700" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-wrap: wrap;letter-spacing: 0.578px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QGHX4EaTS3AknUHvnayNiaLnANlsxF3g1JR5q9HIdppdNd8c8uyuC05w/640?wx_fmt=png"></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">迁移到&nbsp;IPv6，困难重重</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">话虽如此，在真实尝试过程中，<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">DevOps 工程师 Mathew Duggan 坦言，还是被迁移到 IPv6 所遇见困难吓到了：“<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">几乎没有任何东西可以开箱即用。主要的依赖程序立即停止运行，而变通方法也无法满足生产需要。</span><strong><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">团</span></strong><strong><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">队向 IPv6 迁移的过程非常坎坷，这主要是因为几乎没有人做过这项工作。我们多年来都没有做这项工作，现在我们需要付出代价。</span></strong>”</span></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mathew&nbsp;Duggan 尝试<span style="letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">将自己的博客</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">（</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;">https://matduggan.com/ipv6-is-a-disaster-and-its-our-fault/</span><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">）</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">迁移到 IPv6，使用 CDN 管理 IPv4 流量。</span></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">他表示，“实际设置过程很简单。我配置了一个 Debian 设备，并选择了 ‘IPv6’。然后，我得到了第一个‘惊喜’。这台设备没有获得 IPv6 地址，只是得到了一个 /64 的地址，即 18,446,744,073,709,551,616。好消息是，我的小型 ARM 服务器可以通过扩展，在所有公共地址上运行我曾工作过的每家公司所有网络基础设施。“</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">然而当他尝试像普通服务器一样设置它时，问题来了。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;"><strong>问题一：无法通过 SSH（Secure Shell Protocol）登录</strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">「这是一个可以预见的问题」，<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mathew&nbsp;Duggan 说道，</span>这是因为他工作或家里的 ISP 都不支持 IPv6，所以才需要设置自己的服务器，但现在却完全不起作用。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">于是，<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mathew&nbsp;Duggan 只能</span>先附加一个 IPv4 地址，然后通过 SSH 登录，再设置 Cloudflared 来运行隧道。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">让他失望的是，Cloudflare 系统并不会自行处理其中的转换工作。所以删除 IPv4 地址时，隧道意外崩溃了。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">默认情况下，Cloudflared 工具使用的是 IPv4，我们需要编辑 systemd 服务文件，添加：--edge-ip-version 6。这样，隧道才能正常启动，<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mathew&nbsp;Duggan&nbsp;</span>也能通过 SSH 登录了。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;"><strong>问题 2：无法使用 GitHub</strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">当 <span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mathew&nbsp;Duggan&nbsp;的服务器开始运行后，他尝试</span>运行服务器设置脚本时，结果立刻就报错了。它正在尝试访问 hishtory 的安装脚本，这是一个很棒的 shell 历史工具。它试图从 GitHub 提取安装文件，但失败了。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mathew&nbsp;Duggan 产生了疑惑，</span>“这肯定不对。GitHub 一定支持 IPv6？”<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">。</span><br></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">结果意外发现这个整个互联网都在用的发布软件服务 GitHub 竟然不支持 IPv6。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">最后迫于无奈，<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mathew&nbsp;Duggan&nbsp;</span>使用了 TransIP Github 代理服务器，效果还不错。但是随后 Python 出现了 urllib.error.URLError 错误：&lt;urlopen error [Errno 101] Network is unreachable&gt;。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">“<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">好吧，我放弃了。</span>我猜 Debian 中的 Python 3 版本不喜欢 IPv6，但我现在没心情排查它”，<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mathew&nbsp;Duggan 说道</span>。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;"><strong>问题 3 ：无法设置 Datadog</strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">接下来，<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mathew&nbsp;Duggan 想</span>设置 Datadog 来监控这台服务器。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">Bug 再次出现，当他访问 Datadog，登录并开始操作时，系统立即崩溃了。他只是简单设置是运行</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">curl -L https://s3.amazonaws.com/dd-agent/scripts/install_script_agent7.sh</span><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">，现在 S3 支持 IPv6，那么问题究竟出在哪里？</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">经过排查，<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mathew&nbsp;Duggan 发现问题</span>不是出现在 S3 或服务器上，因为他可以正常使用 AWS 提供的 S3 连接测试。后来他通过 apt 手动操作解决了问题。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">直至此时，Mathew&nbsp;Duggan 清晰地感知到，<strong>纯使用 IPv6 根本没有前途。如果不上代理和技术补丁，那几乎没有什么东西能正常工作。</strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">后来，为了从 IPv6 访问 IPv4 资源，他选用了NAT64 服务（</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">https://nat64.net/</span><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">）作为支持。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">此外，他也查找了很多工具，结果发现大多数工具都已经失效，如下列表单中的 Dresel 链接无法工作；Trex 在测试中出现了问题；August Internet 彻底消失；大多数 Go5lab 测试设备离线；Tuxis 倒是可以工作，但在 2019 年推出之后似乎就没升级过。只有一个 Kasper Dupont 支持度还是可以的。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100064887" data-ratio="0.11428571428571428" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="700" style="font-size: 15px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Q3hdXZlicTdZH0gDHXnpe9sZjuIdKFqdo93tKQ8icc5U5JcMkFHiadezlA/640?wx_fmt=png"></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">IPv6 的普及任重而道远</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">在 Paul Copplestone 和 Mathew Duggan 看来，现在虽然已经到了向 IPv6 迁移的时期，但是大多数基础设施和软件还没有为这种变化做好准备。Duggan 警告称，需要针对 IPv6 进行培训和准备，这将是数字专业人员面临的重大挑战。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">对此，也有不少开发者感同身受，来自 HN 上的网友纷纷吐槽道：<br></span></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1" style="list-style-type: square;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">“我仍然在诅咒 IPv6 的设计者没有让它向后兼容 IPv4。IPv6 的设计无疑更好，但由于缺乏向后兼容性，向 IPv6 过渡绝对是个大难题。我知道设计者认为过渡只需要几年时间，但将近 30 年过去了......我们还是在这。”</span></p></li><li style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">IPv6 并不能真正解决地址耗尽的问题，除非 IPv6 地址成为一等公民，而只有当我们不再需要依赖 IPv4 地址时才会发生这种情况。</span></p></li></ul><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">那么不迁移到 IPv6，停留在 IPv4 上，它可能无法满足日益增长的需求，导致性能下降和服务不稳定，同时许多组织采用 NAT 技术来共享有限的 IPv4 地址，这也为其增加了网络管理的复杂性，可能导致一些应用程序或服务的功能受限。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">基于此，越来越多的组织加入到实施 IPv6 迁移的浪潮之中。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 8px;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;">来源：</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;">https://supabase.com/blog/ipv6</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;">https://matduggan.com/ipv6-is-a-disaster-and-its-our-fault/</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: 